""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""
" Change paging overlap amount from 2 to 5 (+3)
" if you swapped C-y and C-e, and set them to 2, it would
" remove any overlap between pages
""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""
